text: Mayra Valdés González (born 22 September 1975) is a Mexican politician from the National Action Party. From 2010 to 2012 she served as Deputy of the LXI Legislature of the Mexican Congress representing Coahuila. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Coahuila Category:Women members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:Members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:National Action Party (Mexico) politicians Category:21st-century Mexican politicians Category:21st-century Mexican women politicians
